	<h2>Collist</h2>
	<p>
		Collist is a responsive layout system that allows you to arrange a list of elements in a grid-like fashion. To use it, simply add the <code>collist</code> class to a <code>ul</code>. Like col, class <code>row-n</code> (where <code>n</code> is 1-12) provides a base width. You can then follow this with classes that specify how many qubase-items to display per row at particular breakpoints. For example, the class <code>md-row-3</code> will show 3 qubase-items per row for viewport widths greater than the <coede>md</coede> breakpoint. Greater breakpoints take precedence over smaller ones.
	</p>

